{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338550/extras/heading-prologue-en.png?t=1736990749\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Alma's in a tight spot -- she's a magical researcher, but has no funds for her research! She's got no choice but to head to the tavern and take on a commission... but the one she ends up with is suspiciously short on details.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Enticed by the reward money, she sets out to meet the mysterious client...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338550/extras/heading-gameplay-en.png?t=1736990749\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338550/extras/gif-01.gif?t=1736990749\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This is a traditional, turn-based RPG. Since Alma is a mage, you'll be using magic to blast your enemies!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">After you beat the game, you can start again with all the levels, money, and spells you acquired the first time around!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">When your TP hits 100 during battle, you can unleash a Magical Boost (M-Boost)!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Alma's magic power, evasion, and accuracy will go into overdrive, and she'll be able to use special spells for the duration! However, MP cost for spells is increased by 50%!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Choose just the right time for an M-Boost, and even the most fearsome foes don't stand a chance!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338550/extras/heading-character-en.png?t=1736990749\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_